        "获得成功",
        "获悉此事"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "獲"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "古代对奴婢的贱称",
      "examples": [
        "臧获"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "獲"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
